red with farms. Its largest city is Burlington, pop. 42,417. Among the state's major exports are cheese, maple syrup, marble, slate, and granite.\"},{\"insert\":\"\\n\\n\"},{\"attributes\":{\"image\":\"http://blypix.com/Art/Wallpaper/images/new_england_fall_2009_3862_wallpaper.jpg\"},\"insert\":1},{\"insert\":\"\\n\"}]}"
